<strong>Revisiting Research</strong><br/>
¬†

We invite you to revisit this<strong> STEG synthesis paper</strong> by <em>Mary Hallward-Driemeier</em> as a useful synthesis of recent structural transformation and economic growth literature and its application to Sub-Saharan Africa, especially in the post-COVID world.

<br/>
<a href="https://steg.cepr.org/publications/structural-transformation-and-economic-growth-10-policy-priorities-africa-post-covid" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Structural Transformation and Economic Growth: 10 Policy Priorities for Africa in the Post-COVID World | STEG (cepr.org)</a><br/>
<br/>
<a href="https://steg.cepr.org/publications/structural-transformation-and-economic-growth-10-policy-priorities-africa-post-covid" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img height="337" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Xan4NSGlDTntgzgZRyFV9yRbRuwCne3eNEFWXFQAfsQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9tY3VzZXJjb250ZW50LmNvbS9iYjI1M2QyOGNiMDVkMzcxOWM5ZTBjOTYwL2ltYWdlcy80OTRhNmE4My0wODg3LTY0ZDgtMWNjYy1lZDhjMDA0NzhlOTMucG5n" width="600" loading="lazy"/></a>







